<fragment>
    <set-body><![CDATA[<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>TXT TV - Page Not Found</title>
    <style>
body {
    background-color: #000;
    color: #0f0;
    font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.4;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 20px;
    min-height: 100vh;
}
.header {
    background-color: #f00;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 10px;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.page-number {
    color: #ff0;
    font-weight: bold;
}
.content {
    white-space: pre-wrap;
    word-wrap: break-word;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    color: #f00;
}
nav {
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 10px;
    background-color: #333;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
}
button {
    background-color: #00f;
    color: #fff;
    border: 2px solid #0ff;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
    font-size: 14px;
}
button:hover {
    background-color: #0ff;
    color: #000;
}
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <span class="page-number">ERROR</span> - PAGE NOT FOUND
    </div>
    <div id="content">
        <pre class="content">PAGE NOT FOUND
==============

The requested page does not exist.

Available pages: 100-120

Please check the page number and try again,
or return to the home page.

---
TXT TV - Error Service</pre>
    </div>
    <nav>
        <button hx-get="/page/100" hx-target="body" hx-push-url="true">Go to Page 100</button>
    </nav>
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/htmx.org@1.9.10"></script>
</body>
</html>]]></set-body>
</fragment>
